{"tid":2005143,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星Exynos 1000曝光 AMD GPU 性能吊打恐怖蘋果A13處理器","createTime":"2020-05-07T02:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T08:39:35.000Z","uid":141060,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"a440da9290bca92ca7e3b52cf7668db39dd958bc","tid":2005143,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:12:52.000Z","msg":"019年，三星和AMD宣布達成合作，未來Exynos處理器將採用AMD定制的移動版Radeon GPU。最近，新的Exynos處理器終於有了消息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qP4DWMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqP4DWMZ.jpg&h=ea1920e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近段時間，採用AMD RDNA架構GPU的最新Exynos處理器（目前稱為Exynos 1000）的基準測試成績曝光。從這份洩露的數據來看，Exynos 1000的GPU性能可以說非常恐怖：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nManhattan 3.1測試為181.8fps（驍龍865 Adreno 650為123fps）<br />\n<br />\nAztec Normal測試為138.25fps（驍龍865 Adreno 650為53fps）<br />\n<br />\nAztec High測試為58fps（驍龍865 Adreno 650為20fps）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h5XqBM4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh5XqBM4.png&h=3c3fbc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡單來說，在AMD RDNA架構的加持下，Exynos 1000在GPU方面暴打了當前Android陣營最強的GPU（當然，可能還會有製程工藝領先的因素），甚至也已經超過了手機領域最強的GPU&mdash;&mdash;A13 Bionic的自研四核GPU。"},{"pid":"a999d883c82648264a46da8b7be57982901aae9a","tid":2005143,"uid":109923,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"三星「首席」打手仲慢過我出post<br />\n真係連打手都廢過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［Exynos 仲未死得？］三星、AMD 聯手打造新一代 Exynos 處理器，AMD加持效能完勝高通<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2005121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2005121</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f7f01c1ecd573494edb210cab21da08655e0be59","tid":2005143,"uid":141060,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"a999d883c82648264a46da8b7be57982901aae9a","tid":2005143,"uid":109923,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020